flowchart TD
    A[User Requests URL] --> B[Server Receives HTTP Request]
    B --> C[Route Matched on Server]
    C --> D[Fetch Required Data from API or DB]
    D --> E[Run Framework renderToString]
    E --> F[Generate Complete HTML String]
    F --> G[Serialize Dehydrated State into Script Tag]
    G --> H[Send HTML Response to Browser]
    H --> I[Browser Parses and Paints HTML Immediately]
    I --> J[Browser Downloads JS Bundle]
    J --> K[Hydration — Attach Event Listeners]
    K --> L[Page Fully Interactive]
    style I fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style L fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
